                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <desc type="Unclear"/>
                           <locus target="#1v"/>
                           <desc>The note is in Amharic and begins as follows: 
                              <q xml:lang="gez">
                                 መምሬ፡ ወልደ፡ ሚካኤልና፡ ገብሩ፡ ጽድቅ፡
                              </q>.
                           </desc>
                        </item> 
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <desc type="ProtectivePrayer">ጸሎተ፡ ሥርየት፡</desc>
                           <locus from="2r" to="4r"/>
                           <desc>The incipit of the text is rubricated. The handwriting deteriorates from <locus target="#2v"/>. 
                              Some lines have been effaced on <locus target="#3r"/>. 
                              The prayer begins as follows: 
                              <q xml:lang="gez">
                                 በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ጸሎተ፡ ሥርየት ወመድኃኒተ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወመንጽሔ፡ ኃጢአት።
                              </q>.
                            </desc>
                        </item> 
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <desc type="CalendaricNote">List of the 'lucky' (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ጽንዕት፡</foreign>) days for each month</desc>
                           <locus target="#4v"/>
                              <desc/>
                        </item> 
                     </list>
                  </additions>
                  
